title: Rate PUF – PY2025
description: The Rate PUF (Rate-PUF) is one of the files that comprise the Health Insurance Exchange Public Use Files. The Rate-PUF contains plan-level data on rates based on an eligible subscriber’s age, tobacco use, and geographic location; and family-tier rates.
